{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"url"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL to process.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Test device registration","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Deep link tracking","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications"}]}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"title":"handleOpenURL:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","